---
title: Creamy Squash Ravioli with Mushrooms and Spinach
description: Is it even possible to say no to rich butternut squash-stuffed ravioli and hearty mushrooms? Certainly not when they're cloaked in a velvety cream sauce and topped with handfuls of Parmesan!
